Accomplishments:

Build Automation: Completed the build.ps1 PowerShell script to automate image tagging, versioning, and cleanup.

Refactoring: Successfully isolated the application source from local Mac environments (venv, .mypy_cache).

Roadblock:

Infrastructure Gap: The target Windows Server does not have the Docker engine installed. Build and deployment commands are currently non-functional on the host.

Proposed Resolution:

Initiate the installation of Docker EE (Enterprise Edition) via the Microsoft Package Provider.

Evaluate Podman as a secondary container engine if a daemon-less, rootless architecture is preferred for security compliance on Windows Server.
